data.description: Discover a captivating 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home in the Lismore community in sought-after Matthews.  This home features an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects living spaces while embracing natural light through expansive windows.  The heart of the home is the exquisite kitchen, boasting a huge island, stainless steel appliances, and a seamless flow into both the dining area and keeping room/breakfast room.  Indulge in indoor-outdoor living on the covered patio, perfect for relaxation or outdoor gatherings amidst lush surroundings.  Music enthusiasts will relish the full surround sound system, enriching the audio experience in seven rooms for entertainment perfection.  Escape to the generous primary bedroom, featuring a private seating area and a spa-like en-suite bathroom with modern fixtures and a lavish tub.  Located in Matthews, this home offers scenic beauty, great location to 485 and convenience to shops. Generac Generator conveys -Media tower is also negotiable.
